      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is geometrically similar to the subject device. Operating conditions (flow rate range, rotational speed, fluid viscosity) span the intended clinical envelope. A formal similarity argument table is provided in the supporting technical report."
    },
    {
