    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index predictions satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all 5 evaluated operating points.",
